variable.name: TISSUE_SITE
variable.description: Body site where sample was collected

variable.name: SAMPLE_TYPE
variable.description: Indicates if sample is derived from tumor or normal cells

variable.name: PRIMARY_METASTATIC_TUMOR
variable.description: Primary tumor, metastasis, or transformed cell line

variable.name: PERCENT TUMOR
variable.description: Indicates the percent of sample representing tumor (tumor purity)

variable.name: HISTOLOGY
variable.description: Histological type of cancer as determined by tumor pathology

variable.name: HISTOLOGIC GRADE
variable.description: Histology grade of cancer as determined by tumor pathology
